          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": " and ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "Psalm 108:1",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": " because it is both the glory of man, for that being endowed with the faculty of speaking, gives him a glory above the brute creatures; and because it is that by which he glorifies God, by ascribing greatness to him, speaking of his marvellous works, and singing his praises, as Christ did, in the great congregation, among his apostles, a little before his death, ",
            "children": []
