        "text": "See on nests, Matthew 8:20. Better, as Rev., dwell. Lit., dwell in a tent or tabernacle. Rendered lodge, Matthew 13:32; Mark 4:32; Luke 13:19. It is a beautiful metaphor. My flesh shall encamp on hope; pitch its tent there to rest through the night of death, until the morning of resurrection.",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "See on nests, ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
